item.title: CVE-2022-27895|2024-09-17T01:06:38.475Z -- palantir -- foundry%20build2
item.description: Information Exposure Through Log Files vulnerability discovered in Foundry when logs were captured using an underlying library known as Build2. This issue was present in versions earlier than 1.785.0. Upgrade to Build2 version 1.785.0 or greater.
